Package com.team3824.akmessing1.scoutingapp.fragments.TeamView

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TeamMatchData
    The fragment for the team view which shows match data statistics in a tabular format.
    TeamNotes
    The fragment for the Team View which displays notes created by match scouts, super scouts, and the drive team.
    TeamPitData
    The fragment for the team view which displays the pit scouting data
    TeamSchedule
    The fragment for the team view which display what matches a team is in as buttons that lead to the match view.
    TeamVisuals
    The fragment that shows the match data in a visual/graphical format for looking at trends.
